	* Makeconf (cleantarg): Add `$(libname)_pic.a'.
	[$(makemode) = library] (targets): Likewise.
	($(libname)_pic.a): New rule.
	($(libdir)/$(libname)_pic.a): Extended from the previous _p.a and
	.a rules.
