	(AC_PROG_CC_WORKS_LOCAL): Renamed to hurd_PROG_CC_WORKS.
	* configure.in: Use hurd_PROG_CC instead of AC_PROG_CC_LOCAL.
	(AC_PREREQ): Require 2.12.
